{"tid":510937,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(女性當道) 動作片《戰狼2》女性觀眾超過男性","createTime":"2017-12-27T03:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T04:37:22.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2acea082ce0ca27ed36dffea7af0cb6858c23e12","tid":510937,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:36:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.sohu.com/a/163774063_114885\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sohu.com%2Fa%2F163774063_114885&d=9XDN3Mps%2F8vLzcjwtXctS3adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=591ff476\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sohu.com/a/163774063_114885</a><br />\n<br />\n《戰狼2》票房突破40億 女性觀眾超男性<br />\n2017-08-11 10:49<br />\n<br />\n如之前很多人猜測，《戰狼2》票房終於突破40億大關，創造了中國影史新紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n根據貓眼專業版的實時票房數據，8月11日《戰狼2》實時票房為2798.54萬元， 上映16天累計票房40.16億元。<br />\n<br />\n在此之前，《戰狼2》已經超過《美人魚》成為華語影史票房冠軍，觀影人次突破1億人次。<br />\n<br />\n從貓眼提供的數據來看，觀看《戰狼2》的城市票房TOP1是上海，達到2.04億元。票房最多的是二線城市，達到40.1%。<br />\n<br />\n想看觀眾性別方面，男性占比46%，女性用戶占比54%。<br />\n<br />\n8月18日，《戰狼2》還將上映IMAX 2D版，票房還會繼續走高。"},{"pid":"c6908578ca6300f4d739e71b83b126eeb756ccbf","tid":510937,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded710a47f5f5d4a675efee84796a6e493110f1e","tid":510937,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:38:41.000Z","msg":"証明女人蠢過男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c10f90cfd470cc35521c18982bd86758a81bba","tid":510937,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T03:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ecf5583ccf60611f639c536ea0095f858b783c","tid":510937,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ded710a